title: 12/09/20 HOUR 3 Paul Finebaum
itunes:title: 12/09/20 HOUR 3 Paul Finebaum
description:
Paul Finebaum tells Dan that Ohio St should find a game to play because they are in the Big10 Championship game any ways. Paul agrees with Dan that Ohio St has no need to play again and will still be in the final 4 competing for a national title.
